        "setup": "Onboard through the [Lowe's Developer Portal](https://developer.lowes.com/portal/) or contact the Lowe's partner integration team at [DL-DIST-PLATFORM-LOWESX-TEAM-ALL@lowes.com](mailto:DL-DIST-PLATFORM-LOWESX-TEAM-ALL@lowes.com) to obtain environment-specific `client_id` and `client_secret` for the OAuth 2.0 client-credentials flow. Use the staging token endpoint `POST https://apis-b2b-stage.lowes.com/v1/oauthprovider/oauth2/token` for LowesX APIs, or the provider auth endpoint shown in PROvider Ops docs `POST https://apis-b2b-stage.lowes.com/am/oauth2/realms/vendors/access_token` with `grant_type=client_credentials` and your issued credentials. Staging and production credentials are separate.",
